.com/news/?id=2626&p=.htm|title=‘New Moon’ Shatters Opening Day Record|publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|date=2009-11-21|accessdate=2012-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120530224623/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=2626&p=.htm|archive-date=2012-05-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其電影的首映週票房則達1.584億美元<ref name="BOM-opening" /><ref name="spidey">{{cite journal|first=Carl|last=DiOrio|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/news/e3i1da5db18eb0203bb06464245988651de|title=Batman beats Spidey with $158.4 mil haul|journal=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|publisher=Nielsen Company|date=2008-07-20|accessdate=2008-08-01|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080731023515/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/news/e3i1da5db18eb0203bb06464245988651de|archivedate=2008-07-31|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/weekends/|title=Biggest Opening Weekends at the Box Office|work=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|publisher=Box Office Mojo, LLC|accessdate=2008-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070309023608/http://boxofficemojo.com/alltime/weekends/|archive-date=2007-03-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>（而後被《[[哈利波特：死神的聖物Ⅱ|哈利波特：死神的聖物Ⅱ]]》所超越）<ref>{{cite news|first=Brandon|last=Gray|url=http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3211&p=.htm|title=Weekend Report: 'Harry' Makes History|publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|date=2011-07-18|accessdate=2012-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120518074104/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3211&p=.htm|archive-date=2012-05-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>。首週劇院平均收入36,283美元列歷史總榜上的第五位<ref>{{cite web|url=http://boxofficemojo.com/alltime/weekends/theateravg.htm?page=THTRWAVG&p=.htm|title=TOP WEEKEND THEATER AVERAGES|publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=2011-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110901220201/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/weekends/theateravg.htm?page=THTRWAVG&p=.htm|archive-date=2011-0